value.string:
Defines if the base_price of maching quantity step should be used as unit price for all items (value is False), or if it applies only to items of the range (value is True).

 If this property is set to True, the base_price will be calculated as such :
 if 0->10 products cost 10$, and 11->infinity products cost 9$, in a command of 15 products, the unit base price is 9.6667$, as the 10 first products cost 10$, and the 5 others cost 9$ (and (10*10+5*9)/15 = 9.6667)
